y shall have therein Azw\u00e2jun Mutahharatun (purified mates or wives), (having no menses, stools, urine, etc.) and they will abide therein forever.\n\n(\u09b8\u09c2\u09b0\u09be-\u09ac\u09be\u0995\u09be\u09b0\u09be)"}